-- 
2011-08-18T06:12:12Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-18/northam-platinum-warns-costs-may-continue-to-advance-faster-than-inflation.html
Northam Platinum Ltd. (NHM) , a South
African producer of the metal, said in the current inflationary
environment, “management will be hard-pressed to contain costs
which continue to rise faster than inflation.”  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
